Outbound sales development
If we believe that Aircall product and services may suit the needs of your company, our outbound sales representative may email and/or call you to introduce and discuss our product with you.
Read more
Legal basis
We have a legitimate Interest to contact you within our outbound sales development activities. These activities are a form of direct marketing, where we carefully choose whether we will contact you or not by assessing potential benefits of Aircall product and services for your company. We have a strong belief that your company may benefit from our communication.
