Contact data of the Aircall Contact
Content of communication between Aircall and Aircall Contact
Legal basis
Processing is necessary for legitimate interests pursued by Aircall. We have a strong belief that all individuals interested in the Aircall product ultimately benefit from improvements of the Aircall product performance, incl. its new features.
